## Support

- **Issues / bug reports:** [github.com/archestra-ai/terraform-provider-archestra/issues](https://github.com/archestra-ai/terraform-provider-archestra/issues) — include the resource type, provider version, and a minimal reproducer.
- **Slack community:** [archestra.ai/join-slack](https://archestra.ai/join-slack) — fastest channel for usage questions and to reach the maintainers.
- **Backend / platform issues:** [github.com/archestra-ai/archestra/issues](https://github.com/archestra-ai/archestra/issues) — for problems that turn out to be in the platform itself rather than the provider.
- **Triage:** maintainers are best-effort; reproducers and full error output speed things up substantially.

